body_text:
@limingfan Which version of the repo are you trying to build?
I recommend building 1.0, or if you really need an older version 0.12.
Bazel and TF are both very quickly evolving, and both had to have a lot of backwards/forwards incompatible changes. So older versions may be more difficult to build.

